# Commander Viral Demo — "The Unbreakable Fleet"
# 85-second demo: Saga rollback + circuit breaker + DLQ + crash-safe resume
# Prerequisites: Node.js, pnpm install
# Run: vhs docs/viral-demo.tape

Output docs/assets/commander-viral-demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 680
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set LetterSpacing 1
Set LineHeight 1.15
Set Padding 24
Set BorderRadius 12
Set Framerate 30
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Hide
Type "npx tsx demos/viral-demo.ts"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Show
Sleep 88s
